name: Anna Asti
description:
'''Anna Anatolyevna Dzyuba''' ({{langx|ru|Анна Анатольевна Дзюба}}; {{langx|uk|Ганна Анатоліївна Дзюба|Hanna Anatoliivna Dzyuba}}; born 24 June 1990), known professionally as '''Anna Asti''' (Анна Асти), is a Ukrainian and Russian singer. 

From 2010 to 2021, she was the soloist of the Ukrainian musical duo [[Artik & Asti]]. In 2022, she began her solo career, releasing several singles and a debut album, which became popular in [[Russia]].
